The UNIX System Foundation Set installation is complete.  Applications
and other software sets can be installed using the tools available with
the Foundation Set after the computer is rebooted.

When you press 'ENTER', the computer will be shut down.  Make sure the
boot floppy drive is empty.

After the computer is rebooted, you can set up and try out your mouse.
You will then be asked to create a user account for your UNIX System.

